  m_text: "Notes:\nDate: march 13th 1999, \nTime: 06:00\n\nthe research team at lab
    kal4an was successful in developing gs-4x the unltimate genome sequence for the
    next human evolution. the component was sent for final testing at our meno vil
    lab.\n\nat 0900, meno vil reported they received a shipment of nutty butty fat
    burner pills. the delivery guy messed up. \n \ngs-4x was delivered to meno villa
    owned by Terry manning a small-time gym coach.  as per the sources, he consumed
    gs-4x with his protien shake.\n\nat 20:00 terry manning bench pressed 2000 lbs.\nhe
    found this when his friends were hyping him up to lift 100 lbs.\n\nsince then
    he lives for the hype..."
