  m_text: "congragulations welcome to the 2nd round of Strong Man Trials!\n\nsubject
    \"encourageman\" has proven himself in the first round with enough hype he can
    survive anything\n\nChallenge 2:  Break the mighty meteor\n\nFor the final round,
    encourageman has to break the mighy meteor.\n\nIt was first discovered in the
    jungles of amazon. legends say it landed on earth millions of years ago. \n\nwe
    tried breaking the meteor at our kal4an lab but nothing works.\n\nlets test the
    might of encourageman\nthis final phase deterimines the fate of gs-4x and the
    power of hype\n"
